# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. The web image (see
# deploy/Dockerfile) only needs `renderer/` sources + the committed wasm pkg;
# everything below is either rebuilt in-image, host-only, or irrelevant.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dist-web
target
.git
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/*.log
# Rust workspace + desktop shell are not part of the web image.
crates
src-tauri
